settings.editor: Dr. Gale Anderson earned her BA from California Medical University in 1995 and her MD from the California Medical University in 2001. Following medical school, Dr. Anderson completed her residency  at University of New Jersey Medical Center and two fellowships in Bakersfield General Hospital.

Dr. James Anderson's research is focused on clinical advancements in prenatal care. Several projects are ongoing including those evaluating clinical outcomes and measures of postoperative quality of life.
